QUESTIONS PREVIEW:
Q1. (a) Derive Einstein's A and B coefficients for spontaneous and stimulated emission.
    (b) Describe the construction and working of a He-Ne Laser with energy level diagram.
Q2. (a) Discuss the phenomenon of interference in thin films due to reflected light.
    (b) Explain the theory of Newton's Rings. Show that diameter of dark rings is proportional to square root of natural numbers.
